{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So pullovers were a convenient way of wearing the star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And had on overcoats that we wore, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The interesting thing about it, which I found out later on, really, because many of these things I don't really remember, but [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] an interesting item is how I remember all this long.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave a talk recently to a school in Hampshire with Stephen Smith, actually.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came to the question period, there was a young boy of about 12.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, sir, how do you remember all this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I was a bit taken aback by the question, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I managed to answer it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, basically, there are some things which I shall always remember, like the 10th of May, 1940, and even the 23rd of August, when-- when these two boys had their birthdays, and that we lived in Berlin, and that we lived in Tempelhof, and that there was an airport there.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there are lots of things that I shall always remember forever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, there are lots of things that I've remembered by talking to my brother, Richie.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we stimulate each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We say there was this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he said, oh yeah, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then there was that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow, between us, when we've done taped interviews between ourselves for [INAUDIBLE] kind of thing, we stimulate each other into remembering things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Memory is a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd not realized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because of the fact, when I say, I-- I never remember this thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If Richie says to me, you remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On Friday night, we had the service.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And mother lit the candles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's-- I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But very often, with things like that, it comes back into my memory then.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
